def_cn: 丘比特(罗马神话中的爱神)
def_en: Cupid is the Roman god of love. He is usually shown as a baby boy with wings and a bow and arrow.

def_cn: 爱神丘比特的画像(或雕像)
def_en: A cupid is a picture or statue of a pretty little boy with wings, often holding a bow and arrow.
